Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:33.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人更該HIGH 完美社會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:41.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是明日的超級明星 今晚一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:50.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（孔明，照亮前路）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 那位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,近藤剛氏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這音樂節的主辦者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,參與策劃了國內外諸多大型音樂節的製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是音樂節界的泰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種大腕竟然來這角落裡的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該不會是因為我們擅自增加照明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以來處罰我們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝您專程前來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問要來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 別多此一舉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,初次參加 而且還是在E15舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:34.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,史無前例地吸引到了這麼多觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,外貌也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:39.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,社交網路上也有不少人發文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:43.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（E15人暴多）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（E15人暴多）\NE15人暴多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（每年都有樂隊參戰，但這次是史上最多！在冷門舞台創造了奇蹟！）\NE15人暴多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,每年都有樂隊參戰 但這次是史上最多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在冷門舞台創造了奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這人我追定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO歌聲超好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:54.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總的來說評價很積極
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望EIKO小姐可以再次參加我舉辦的音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:03.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,出演藝術音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搶走JET JACKET的觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逆風取勝 讓英子收穫自信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,甚至還吸引了近藤的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓他安排下一場演出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這傢伙果然不是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在你身上感受到了巨大的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:33.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們想為你準備一個特別的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪有 就我這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡有兩張名片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這張是福岡音樂節負責人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將於一個月後舉辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,規模跟這次一樣 約有一萬觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:05:01.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,另一邊是去年流量30萬人的大型夏季音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,SUMMER SONIA的歌手負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請拿走你想參加的一方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說起SUMMER SONIA音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,規模放眼全國都是最大級的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子能跟一流歌手同台表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就我這種歌手真的能參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 既然有機會出場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那還是SUMMER SONIA更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,出演SUMMER SONIA的前提條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須參加「靠10萬讚獲得出演權」企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是我們為看好的歌手準備的企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要在期限內獲得10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能出演SUMMER SONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我聽說過這個企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有團體讚不夠 直接就解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有偶像為了博讚不顧吃相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被噴到銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,高關注度是把雙刃劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:08.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一旦失敗就會失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,順便一提 這個企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,五年來只有一個團體達標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我看看…我最多的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:22.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才得到了大約1400讚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬肯定不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就參加福岡的音樂節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以吧 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只管盡全力支持你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論這條路是多麼艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:45.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的夢想是出道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是吸引一萬名觀眾？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 你要想清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬讚的企劃風險太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:53.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我的夢想是參加全球最大的音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-等於是單槍匹馬殺進大軍 算了吧\N-我的夢想是參加全球最大的音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我的夢想是參加全球最大的音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Voiceleland
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 英子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,選福岡的音樂節吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這邊 選這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可不能拖下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只能選SUMMER SONIA吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣選是正確的吧 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:26.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你太讓我著迷了 EIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I have a crush on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是「特來電」的俚語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 我會跟負責人打招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,期待在SUMMER SONIA的會場見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:52.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是可以正常說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,SUMMER SONIA…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,事已至此 我肯定會全力支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但你準備怎樣集到10萬讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明肯定能想辦法搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為這有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,NO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:28.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你剛才那語氣明顯是有自信搞定吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來只是痴人說夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:31.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我的夢想完蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我的夢想完蛋了！-我意思是照現狀來看很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有件事我已經想很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:46.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天時地利人不和 此為逆人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:51.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是說 現在需要新的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:51.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人才？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,需要具備熾熱的氣場（vibes）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:56.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,vibes？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以及能操縱敵人的感染力（flow）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,flow？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們要招攬強大的說唱歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼是…說唱歌手？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,230 163
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,358
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,557
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,45…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:28.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,45？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我為什麼上傳了這張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然1400就是巔峰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老闆 好憔悴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一想到要集10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就死活睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行了 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須立刻做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須採取點行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,否則會被10萬壓垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明應該想了辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:05.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還不是因為猜不透孔明的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該死 無法否認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬…讚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:14.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把孔明找來問問吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明沒在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在外面跟別人聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說孔明 你今天也穿這身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你有多少套同樣的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好兇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 我自拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夠頂吧 今天必須開早趴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 早上的派對是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可沒開玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗨到昏厥那種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最好先喝點魔爪備戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行了 太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,換個方式自拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都答應別人一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有心情玩啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 這都沒怎麼準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬上就要開門營業了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:55.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,改天再開個早趴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又要麻煩你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我負責的舞池打掃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我接下來還得赴約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在可是凌晨4點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天還請見諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太狠了 早上的孔明好來電
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後面交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你可以下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要再干會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 那傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（SUMMER SONIA 10萬人點讚企劃舉辦中！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幹好能幹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:47.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怪了 我聽說他借用了店裡的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是英子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放假還來店裡 真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一次聽這麼多歌 能聽出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:08.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（※ 聖德太子是日本古代皇子 相傳其聽力過人）\N嗯 就是遠不及聖德太子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說回來 英子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你找我有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最近都沒跟你聊過幾句 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是好奇你放假時在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,昨天我夜觀星象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,北斗七星的光芒很強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:36.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,星塵由南至東 劃出了一縷弧線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,根據占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在澀谷以東
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,六本木似乎凝聚著大量的「氣」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 這意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有隕石要墜落了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚六本木一帶會極其熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想去那邊的俱樂部轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然只是想去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦？孔明人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才跟英子一起去六本木玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還帶上英子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明那小子到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對六本木不太熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼今晚就由我來當嚮導吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可以先去一趟堂吉訶德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想不到當面還挺難說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呃 哪裡熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不可操之過急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來這只是為了喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在優惠時間段1000日元隨便喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既不浪費軍費
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還能聽到流行歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？在六本木也能花小錢喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們就在這裡好好預熱身心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:03.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嘿 孔明 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都混熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗨 可愛的女孩 你是他女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是的 孔明是我的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,噢 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更像是製作人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,顧問？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但這怎麼看都是在玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底算什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 還是挺滿足的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼要招攬說唱歌手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,時機一到自然就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是的 這樣說就太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟騙子占卜師一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說孔明本職是占卜師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請稱我為軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 去下一家店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下一家才是今晚的主戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四天王？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是主戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,V3俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然是個有名的搭訕夜場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過DJ的水準很高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是個業內人士也會來的人氣店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都穿得好奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:19.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,裝扮自己 威嚇敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,過去孟獲率領的象兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也裝扮得無比花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孟獲與我軍交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敗陣 求饒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整整重複了七遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是個難纏的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要繼續聊這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是太失禮了 一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不對 我穿這身是不是來錯地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我早料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（耶）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才在堂吉訶德準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就用小飾品脫穎而出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你其他部分顯眼過頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是孔明嗎 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好久沒見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這傢伙都混熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說 你這眼鏡也太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,挺帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在哪買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-我要買個一樣的 -真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還挺適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那不是DJ「HAJIMARI」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來回日本了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:34.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好嘛 我自己玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（TSURUTANTON烏冬）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,通完宵吃烏龍麵 真香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你喜歡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說你自己跑了 太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得我們現在沒時間玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬讚企劃也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們還沒談過該怎麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛才在俱樂部裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我獲得了某個重要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於有望找到苦尋的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:22.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為我們離達成10萬讚企劃近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,前面的所作所為也是為了這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來你付出了不少努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你會擔心也在情理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我想了不少計策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但都是時機一到自然明白的計策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:51.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是想讓你專注於唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:52.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 要我說多少次都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:02.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的歌聲深深打動了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會盡全力支持你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那可以答應我一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起去Voiceleland吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:17.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全球最大規模的電子舞曲音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要參加這個音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就意味著必須成為世界級歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是第一個聽我說出夢想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唉 說出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,10萬讚就怕得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:36.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就我這樣的人 是不是痴人說夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:42.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,首先該改掉妄自菲薄的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妄自菲薄？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請再自信點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 成下意識的習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣說自己怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妄自菲薄 束縛自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這可不是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:02.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我啊 小時候總是跟爸爸一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是他某一天突然就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過我想著只要堅持做音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們之間就能保持聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果這次換成媽媽強烈反對我做音樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可能是從那時候開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就沒自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就這樣持續了一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我萬念俱灰時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我遇上了老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看了瑪麗亞·迪賽兒的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後我就想著 我只剩音樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要靠音樂活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到最後都沒能割捨對音樂的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想參加Voiceleland
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那樣或許就能實現夢想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就像魚需要水一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:59.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想必對英子來說 音樂必不可少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:02.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這叫水乳交融
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,水餃真神？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是水乳交融
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,指的是不可或缺的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:14.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那孔明跟我也是水餃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:15.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說我很看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你想走的路並不平坦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以 你今晚願意向我袒露心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪有 哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你我是一蓮托生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:40.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還請允許我陪你走完這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也不知道能不能幫忙收穫10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我寫了首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你願意聽聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我早看出你有事瞞著我 原來是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:11.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（歌曲-11-ok）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反反覆覆的Every day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:17.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連哭泣都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:20.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將失去色彩的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:24.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即使遍體鱗傷 It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:31.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將傷痕當成勳章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:32.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Live your life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:36.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So you want to be free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能聽見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:45.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,勇敢面對逆風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:49.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,風強豈不正好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:52.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:58.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,BEAUTIFUL DREAMER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:01.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,發現Your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:05.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想緊擁在懷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:08.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,飛向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（BEAUTIFUL DREAMER）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:12.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（BEAUTIFUL DREAMER）\N英子 這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:13.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（沒什麼可失去的）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（沒什麼可失去的）\N彷彿能鼓舞聽歌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:15.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（沒什麼可失去的）\N簡直就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:16.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（找回自我）\N簡直就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:17.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（找回自我）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:19.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（找回自我）\N真是的 很難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:21.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）\N好好聽 別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）\N10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:24.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）\N無論如何都要達標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:26.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（展翅高飛 順應心聲）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（重獲新生）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:28.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（重獲新生）\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:28.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（重獲新生）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（重獲新生）\N看來今晚的六本木果然極其熱情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:33.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（You're like a butterfly）\N看來今晚的六本木果然極其熱情啊
